title: Asian-Style Street Food Kit with Prawn Banh Mi, Pork Larb Lettuce Cups & Chicken Satay | Serves 2+
description: Indulge in the bold flavours of Asia with our street food kit! Whip up a pork larb lettuce cups brimming with zesty pork, alongside prawn banh mi and chicken satay for an unforgettable culinary adventure that brings the vibrant essence of street-side favourites straight to your table.
